to the observatory.

126
00:10:36,594 --> 00:10:38,471
What can I show you?

127
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:41,390
We're supposed to land soon.

128
00:10:41,682 --> 00:10:43,017
[chuckles]

129
00:10:44,226 --> 00:10:47,063
