What can I show you?

131
00:10:51,317 --> 00:10:52,693
Show me Homestead II.

132
00:10:52,777 --> 00:10:56,030
Homestead II is the fourth
planet in the Bhakti System.

133
00:10:56,197 --> 00:10:58,366
Right. And where are we?

134
00:10:58,449 --> 00:11:01,452
We're in transit
from Earth to Homestead II.

135
00:11:01,619 --> 00:11:04,372
We will arrive in approximately
90 years.

136
00:11:04,455 --> 00:11:05,456
What?

137
00:11:05,539 --> 00:11:08,876
We arrive at Homestead II
in 90 years, three weeks,
and one day.

138
00:11:08,959 --> 00:11:10,169
No. Wait.

139
00:11:10,252 --> 00:11:11,879
How long ago
did we leave Earth?

140
00:11:12,046 --> 00:11:14,548
Approximately 30 years ago.

141
00:11:18,511 --> 00:11:20,221
I woke up too soon.

142
00:11:23,057 --> 00:11:24,100
