are sent by laser array.

145
00:11:28,312 --> 00:11:29,772
This is an expensive service.

146
00:11:30,106 --> 00:11:31,732
-Bite me.
-Happy to help.

147
00:11:34,693 --> 00:11:35,820
[Avalon] Planet and connection?

148
00:11:35,903 --> 00:11:37,863
Earth. The Homestead Company.

149
00:11:38,072 --> 00:11:42,576
There are 30,826 contacts
listed under Homestead Company.

150
00:11:42,952 --> 00:11:45,996
I'm emigrating to Homestead II
and I have an emergency.

151
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,248
I have a customer help line.

152
00:11:47,331 --> 00:11:48,416
Sounds about right.

153
00:11:48,916 --> 00:11:49,917
