154
00:11:51,085 --> 00:11:53,754
Hi. I'm Jim Preston.

155
00:11:54,588 --> 00:11:56,090
I'm a passenger on the Avalon.

156
00:11:56,924 --> 00:11:58,050
I...

157
00:12:01,303 --> 00:12:04,181
I think something went wrong
with my hibernation pod.

158
00:12:04,265 --> 00:12:05,641
I woke up too soon.

159
00:12:05,724 --> 00:12:09,395
And I mean, way too soon.

160
00:12:09,478 --> 00:12:12,022
Nobody else is awake, and...

161
00:12:12,731 --> 00:12:14,275
I don't know how to get
back to sleep.

162
00:12:14,483 --> 00:12:17,611
And the thing is,
there's 90 years to go.

163
00:12:20,906 --> 00:12:23,242
At this rate, I'm...

164
00:12:27,121 --> 00:12:29,540
