I'm trying to fix this.

165
00:12:29,665 --> 00:12:32,084
Maybe I missed something.
I could use a hand.

166
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:34,545
That's all.

167
00:12:35,629 --> 00:12:36,630
Thank you.

168
00:12:38,007 --> 00:12:39,300
