malfunctions?

197
00:14:04,385 --> 00:14:06,887
Hibernation pods are fail-safe.

198
00:14:07,012 --> 00:14:08,222
They never malfunction.

199
00:14:08,305 --> 00:14:09,557
Well, I woke up early.

200
00:14:09,974 --> 00:14:11,141
Can't happen.

201
00:14:11,725 --> 00:14:13,602
How long until we get
to Homestead II?

202
00:14:13,769 --> 00:14:15,479
About 90 years or so.

203
00:14:15,563 --> 00:14:17,648
And when are all the passengers
supposed to wake up?

204
00:14:17,731 --> 00:14:19,567
Not till the last four months.

205
00:14:20,568 --> 00:14:22,486
How is it that I'm sitting
here with you

206
00:14:23,237 --> 00:14:24,947
